Subject: [PATCH] drm/xe: introduce xe_gt_reset and xe_gt_wait_for_reset
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 5db89168c408871d306e9fb669e494a1444da8ee
